<br>
Since I don't play much anymore, another spot..we'll 2 is in Natimbi.  Those ghost for the FT neck and then off into water after err, mermaid thingies.  Potameids?  Named drops a decent sellable monk/bst item with particle effect or melee neck.<br>
<br>
Also, if you can handle it, go to Siren's Grotto.  Zone in from CS, invis up, but watch for see invis...hang a right in water...hang another right..and your in a little spot for Fellspine.  Work him for spiked seahorse hide belt or what not.  I still wear it but sells on my server for around 35k.<br>
<br>
Finally, and once again this may be server specific, is Chardok.  You can, once achieving good faction here, kill the proverbial two birds with one stone.  Hobbit mask+pp camp.  Look here for somewhat outdated but still relavent material: <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://amazon.uptimenet.com/guides/newchardok.htm" target="top">amazon.uptimenet.com/guides/newchardok.htm</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
